sources.title: Wallaby Jim of the Islands
sources.description: Pearls, pretty girls and an evil rival give Wallaby Jim a tough time in the South Sea Islands.

sources.title: Wallaby Jim of the Islands (1937) JUNGLE ADVENTURE
sources.description:
Stars: George Houston, Ruth Coleman, Douglas Walton
Director: Charles Lamont

Wallaby Jim and his men have just found a priceless source of pearls in the South Pacific. But when an associate puts the whole operation in jeopardy, an unscrupulous rival decides to exploit the situation by jumping Jim's claim!

sources.title: Wallaby Jim of the Islands (1937) Adventure, Drama, Music Full Length Movie
sources.description:
HIGH ADVENTURE ON A PIRATE SEA!
Wallaby Jim and his men have just found a valuable source of pearls in the South Pacific, and have to fend off a vicious rival to lay claim to the treasure.

metadata.Plot: Wallaby Jim and his men have just found a valuable source of pearls in the South Pacific. But Jim's associate Norman has put the whole operation in jeopardy because of his gambling problem. Jim's unscrupulous rival Richter decides to exploit the situation by jumping Jim's claim and trying to take over for himself.
